{
  "stem": "10829.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then as when they finished, when they finished, they had killed you out, then they-- on the following day, you-- you had to go in wherever you had room, and you stayed down there, because you had curfews.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You couldn't go out after-- after it was dark.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You couldn't get out of the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Mom and I, my mother would handle the children's stuff, clothes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's where she used to steal sometimes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She'd steal an extra dress or something for-- for my brother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I used to handle shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had to go around and take the shoes off of them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then we threw them in mass graves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they used to come around in the morning, and they would ask for volunteers, able bodies.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they would take those able bodies and-- no.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "First, before that, they would have some elders go out, and-- especially the Jewish police-- and they would dig graves on the outside of the city.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they would come in with the trucks, and they'd pick up some people, and they would shoot them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And what they were doing, basically, in those days is they were thinning the population.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and they would kill them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the first-- the first group of people that were these that they killed was those Jews who [NON-ENGLISH]-- who told on on the other Jews.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were the turncoats, the [NON-ENGLISH]-- the-- not the spies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They-- they were the ones that were killed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They used to get a lot of the older Jews, and they would say, you tell us where this one is, or where the gold is, or where this, and they had them-- you're going to dig the graves.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they dig the graves, then you're going to be spared.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
